@node intro "Introduction.."

  @{fg shine}@{b}Intro
  ~~~~~@{ub}@{fg text}

   This is a preferences editor for the Mpeg Audio player
   AmigaAMP v2.8+ by Thomas Wenzel.

   I decided to make this as many settings in AmigaAMP could
   only be edited by hand in the config file.

   This prefs editor is now the official prefs editor for AmigaAMP.


@endnode

@node install "Installation.."

  @{fg shine}@{b}Installation
  ~~~~~~~~~~~~@{ub}@{fg text}

   Just copy the file AmigaAMP-Prefs into the same directory
   were AmigaAMP is and do not change the name of it.

   The icon and this guide can be copied anywhere you prefer.


@endnode

@node req "Requirements.."

  @{fg shine}@{b}Requirements
  ~~~~~~~~~~~~@{ub}@{fg text}

   AmigaAMP v2.8+, preferably v2.12+

   OS version 37+

   MUI - Magical User Inteface V3

   Asl.library v37+


@endnode

@node chg "Changes.."

  @{fg shine}@{b}Changes
